OL,3,CFA to name and shame grassroots clubs
OL,4,Cwho fail to curb touchline abuse
OL,6,FReport by Emma Wilkinson
OL,8,FGrassroots football clubs which fail
OL,9,Fto curb abusive touchline behaviour
OL,10,Fwill be named and shamed in a
OL,11,Fcrackdown by the Lincolnshire FA.
OL,13,FThe threat comes after a survey of
OL,14,Fteenage players found less than half
OL,15,Ffelt the behaviour of parents,
OL,16,Fspectators and coaches during games
OL,17,Fwas positive.
