OL,3,CFA to name and shame grassroots clubs
OL,4,Cwho fail to curb touchline abuse
OL,6,FClubs' disciplinary records will also
OL,7,Fbe into account when considering
OL,8,Fapplications for funding.
OL,10,FProf Sir Jonathan Van-Tam, chair of
OL,11,FLincolnshire FA, said the action was
OL,12,Fdesigned to "drive positive change."
OL,14,F"All of this might sound a bit tough,
OL,15,Fbut as I've said before, enough really
OL,16,Fis enough," he said.
