OL,3,CFA to name and shame grassroots clubs
OL,4,Cwho fail to curb touchline abuse
OL,6,F"The vast majority of our clubs are
OL,7,Fwell-run and the vast majority of our
OL,8,Fparticipants do everything they do
OL,9,Fwith respect for others, and genuine
OL,10,Fintegrity. The actions will have only
OL,11,Fa positive impact for them. Together,
OL,12,Fwe can make football in Lincolnshire
OL,13,Fthe best it can possibly be."
OL,15,FThe survey of youth players across the
OL,16,Fcounty found:
