OL,3,CFA to name and shame grassroots clubs
OL,4,Cwho fail to curb touchline abuse
OL,6,FBen Pearce, safeguarding officer at
OL,7,FLincolnshire FA, said: "The youth
OL,8,Ffootball community of Lincolnshire has
OL,9,Fspoken, and we need to listen and act
OL,10,Fwhere we can. Children never cease to
OL,11,Famaze us in the clarity and pertinence
OL,12,Fthey provide when asked their opinion.
OL,14,F"It is clear that children in
OL,15,FLincolnshire love their football and
OL,16,Fwant to enjoy their footballing
OL,17,Fexperience with friends and family
OL,18,Falike.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
